# Recency-trap fixture: cases where the OLDER memory is the correct answer and a
# NEWER memory shares the probe's keywords but is the wrong answer. A recency
# prior that promotes newest-wins blindly will demote the correct old fact below
# the fresh distractor. correct-wins = correct outranks every trap. This is the
# gate the staleness recency prior must survive before its default moves off 0:
# it bounds how hard RecencyWeight can push. See docs/benchmarks.md Phase 3.
